1923;;Bonnie Prince Charlie;;British;;Charles Calvert;;Gladys Cooper, Ivor Novello;;historical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bonnie_Prince_Charlie_(1923_film);;The film depicts the Jacobite Rebellion of 1745 and its aftermath when the Jacobite pretender Charles Edward Stuart evaded capture by the forces loyal to the Hanoverians, and escaped to the Continental Europe with the help of Flora MacDonald.